codex
Implemented A03.

Changed `ModelCallRequest` in [foundation.rs](/Users/will/dev/nunchi/roko/roko/.roko/worktrees/converge-followup-run-20260428-231543-A03/crates/roko-core/src/foundation.rs) to carry the requested metadata fields with `Default` and `#[serde(default)]`, switched `caller` to `Option<String>`, and added serde derives for the request and nested chat/cache types. Kept `CallerIdentity` as a canonical label helper with `Into<String>` so callers do not invent local caller strings.

Extended `FeedbackEvent::ModelCall` with optional observability fields and updated the affected construction/deserialization/JSONL paths across agent, runtime, learn, ACP, CLI, serve, neuro, dreams, and std. Newly added metadata fields are left as `None`/empty at call sites for now, per the Wave C note.

